OrlandoHome › Locations › Orlando 















Orlando
Sugar Factory Orlando is conveniently located on International Drive at the up and coming I-Drive 360 entertainment complex, home of the Orlando Eye.  A celebrity favorite, this American brasserie is sure to satisfy the sweet tooth cravings of both tourists and locals alike.
Upscale dining classics are served from brunch to late-night ranging from decadent crepes to flavorful milkshakes, gourmet burgers, ice cream sandwiches and more.
Signature treats include a number of celebrity-endorsed Couture Pops, smoking Goblet Drinks, candy infused cocktails, and the one-and-only King Kong Sundae with 16 scoops of ice cream, tasty toppings, and even sparklers!
After dinner, guests will want to stay long into the night to enjoy the innovative smoking goblet drinks, top hits dance music, and lively social scene.  The atmosphere is perfect for a girls’ night out, birthday and bachelorette parties, and so much more!
Book now


